Subdivision.SubDescription: Campagna Homes has been building custom homes since 1952 and is honored to be ranked #1 on Houzz.com in the Tampa Bay Area Area. We define success as creating long-lasting relationships. Our clients are happy to share with you their 5-Star Experience before, during, and long after the completion of their custom home. Our promise is to earn a 5-Star review from our clients and everyone who has contact with Campagna Homes. We invite you to join our exclusive client community

Plan.Description: Traditional style home on a large lake, with gardens and fountains. The home was designed so that every room in the house has a view of the lake. There are tennis courts and picnic areas around a large pool.

Mediterranean Tuscan style home that is on the water and has its own beach and dock. This home was designed for coastal living and living life outdoors. Take the elevator to the 2nd floor and enjoy the game room and media room areas. The gourmet kitchen has all high-end appliances. The master bedroom has its own private area and private outdoor area. The home has a 4 car garage.

Beautiful modern waterfront home that boasts a custom wood and glass staircase, open concept great room and kitchen, hurricane impact windows and doors that open up to the intercostal. Large kitchen with custom modern cabinetry and viking appliances. The home also has a media room and home office area.

This exclusive luxury home was built to exacting standards to support a premier lifestyle with signature features. Modern contemporary home that sits on a large lot looking over a golf course. This home has a game room and media room. The master suite is on the second floor and is private from the other rooms. This is a great room style home that flows to the kitchen. The home has a large pool and lanai with a gazebo. The home has an elevator to the second floor.

A modern contemporary waterfront home that has views of the bay. The home has an Infiniti pool and spa with a large lanai and outdoor kitchen area. The great room has high ceilings with floor to ceiling windows everywhere to maximize the views. The home has many textures with wood, metal and stone all working together to create a warm modern sophisticated space. The large kitchen has 2 islands and a hidden pantry. The master bedroom has a private seating area with a large very customized master closet.

Mediterranean style home with lots of space for a large family. Great place for outdoor gatherings with a large lanai, pool area and outdoor kitchen. The home has a media room and game room with a playroom at the second floor. Downstairs there is a large wine room next to the living room and foyer area. The master closet was designed specially after a famous musicians closet.

Mediterranean style home with lot's of stone, marble and precast materials. The home is on a golf course with magnificent views. This home has living spaces for every family member, even the family pets have their own room. This home has a large craft room/ laundry room as well. We created this home to have a porte cache and separate detached garage with a large circle drive and fountain.

A gorgeous 15,000 sq. ft. Mediterranean style home on 10 acres with a separate guest house and separate gym. The home is set on a beautiful lake and has an oversized pool with a cabana and outdoor kitchen area with 2 fireplaces. The game room and media room have their own wing; along with views of the lake. The kitchen has beautiful brick and stone on the walls and connects to the wine room and wine closet; where there is seating and tables to sample wine and other spirits. The home has both his and her offices and a separate library.

Mediterranean style home that sits on the intercostal waterway with views of Dunedin in the distance. The home has a 5 car garage, large family room that opens up to a second story lanai and outdoor fireplace. This home is 3 stories, but don't worry about lugging up the groceries, take the built-in elevator from the garage level up to the living area. The master suite is on the 3rd floor and has its own private balcony.

French Country style home on a golf course with a pool and outdoor kitchen. The home was designed to maximize the view of the golf course. This home has a beautiful staircase and elevator that leads to the second floor. The game room/media room upstairs opens up to a private balcony.
